        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl text-[#1e293b] dark:text-[#e2e8f0] font-bold mb-2">Yaratıcı Yazma Atölyesi</h3>
          <p class="text-[#1e293b]/60 dark:text-[#e2e8f0]/60 text-sm font-medium">10 Mayıs 2024</p>
        </div>
